<doc id="911167" wikidata="Q7688583" url="?curid=911167" title="Tatárjárás (disambiguation)">
<text>Tatárjárás is a Hungarian word, meaning literally &quot;Passing of the Tatars&quot;.

It may refer to:
* The Mongol invasion of Hungary in 1241-42 (see Mongol invasion of Europe).
* An operetta by Emmerich Kálmán, titled in English &quot;The Gay Hussars&quot; or &quot;Autumn Manoeuvres&quot;.
* &quot;Tartar Invasion&quot;, a 1917 Hungarian film</text><links>
