<doc id="911431" wikidata="Q602433" url="?curid=911431" title="Independência total">
<text>&quot;&quot; is the national anthem of São Tomé and Príncipe. The anthem, adopted in 1975, was written by Alda Neves da Graça do Espírito Santo (1926–2010) and composed by Manuel dos Santos Barreto de Sousa e Almeida (born 1933).

